These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, papaya, lettuce, grapefruit
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, rat, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, airplane, roller, tram
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person driving the tram is the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
4. the person eating apple is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person driving the roller and the person eating papaya##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | lettuce | grapefruit  | papaya | apple  |
| Pet         | snake    | chinchilla  | hedgehog       | rat     |
| Transport   | roller     | train | tram       | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, photography, baking, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, horror, drama, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, rowing, biathlon, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person watching crime movies and the person who's hobby is camping##2
5. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the person watching drama movies is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | photography | sudoku    | camping  | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | musical  | horror   | drama    |
| Sport         | rowing | snowboarding | skiing | biathlon      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, filmmaking, fishing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, punk, hip-hop, disco
1. the fan of punk is between the fan of disco and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
6. the fan of soul is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk         | fanta   | hot-chocolate    |
| Hobby         | singing | fishing | puzzles | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | punk        | disco      | soul   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, american, spanish, indonesian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, badminton, ice-hockey, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, motorbike, tram, taxi
1. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the taxi and the indonesian##2
3. the spanish is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the spanish is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | indonesian        | american   | pakistani | spanish |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | baseball | badminton    | volleyball |
| Transport     | tram       | subway     | taxi       | motorbike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, coffee, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, card-games, reading, board-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, surfing, cycling, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking juice##2
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up | iced-tea      | juice       | coffee   |
| Hobby      | fishing   | card-games  | board-games | reading     |
| Sport      | surfing     | weightlifting | cycling        | rowing |

