.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, lettuce, kiwi, artichoke
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, board-games, camping, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, basketball, sailing, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's sport is sailing##2
6. the person eating lettuce is between the person eating raspberry and the person eating kiwi##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | kiwi | lettuce  | raspberry | artichoke      |
| Hobby   | camping  | chess  | reading | board-games |
| Sport   | baseball | golf | basketball | sailing     |

