.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, grapefruit, peach, banana
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, adventure, action, romance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, baseball, ice-hockey, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching action movies##2
7. the person eating banana is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | peach  | grapefruit    | banana | pumpkin  |
| Movie-Genre   | action | romance       | adventure        | superhero    |
| Sport         | baseball | tennis | skiing  | ice-hockey |

