.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, card-games, collecting, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, drama, adventure, zombie
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle, cat, ferret
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person watching drama movies is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | photography  | card-games | collecting | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | zombie | drama   | adventure         |
| Pet           | hedgehog | cat  | turtle   | ferret      |

