1. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is the person eating watermelon##1
3. the fan of metal is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person eating cauliflower##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is between the fan of blues and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | lettuce  | watermelon    | nectarine | cauliflower       |
| Hobby         | reading | baking | magic-tricks  | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | soul      | metal  | rock     |

