1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
2. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
3. the person eating kale is between the person eating peas and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
4. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
7. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is chess##1
8. the person watching romance movies is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
