.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, grapes, cucumber, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, baking, traveling, dancing
4 different pets are kept: hamster, ferret, snake, bird
1. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the owner of the snake is the person eating grapes##1
3. the owner of the hamster is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the owner of the hamster and the person eating plum##2
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is the owner of the bird##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the ferret##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | plum  | cucumber | lettuce | grapes     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | traveling   | dancing  | baking    |
| Pet     | ferret        | bird       | hamster      | snake |

