.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, coffee, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, chess, camping, cooking
4 different pets are kept: lizard, cat, goldfish, rabbit
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking coffee and the person who's hobby is chess##2
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | water | coffee     | hot-chocolate | fanta       |
| Hobby      | camping  | cooking | photography  | chess |
| Pet        | rabbit  | cat      | goldfish        | lizard      |

