3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the mouse##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | sprite  | coffee       | iced-tea   |
| Hobby      | video-games     | photography | cooking | traveling |
| Pet        | mouse        | goat | frog     | chinchilla |

