.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, freelancer, firefighter, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, superhero, thriller, spy
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, train, taxi
1. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the train is the firefighter##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the musician##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the boat is between the person watching thriller movies and the firefighter##2
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the boat is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | freelancer | videographer | firefighter    | musician   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller      | superhero   | spy | scientific |
| Transport     | skateboard     | boat       | train        | taxi    |

