.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, drawing, card-games, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, manager, doctor, chef
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, cricket, climbing, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is the chef##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the software-developer and the person who's hobby is photography##2
6. the doctor is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is cricket##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | card-games   | drawing           | photography         | reading      |
| Job     | software-developer | doctor | chef | manager |
| Sport   | climbing     | cricket         | cycling       | weightlifting        |

