.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, coffee, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, techno, punk, indie
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, british, egyptian, pakistani
1. the fan of house is the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking coffee and the british##2
3. the person drinking coffee is the fan of techno##1
4. the person drinking coffee is between the fan of punk and the pakistani##2
5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the turkish is between the egyptian and the fan of indie##2
7. the fan of house is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice | coffee | milk   | water |
| Music-Genre   | house  | techno    | punk   | indie     |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | egyptian | turkish | british   |

