.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, fanta, sprite
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, mango, kale
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, skiing, badminton
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
2. the person eating mango is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's sport is skiing##2
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | juice | sprite           | fanta |
| Food       | cranberry | mango    | cucumber          | kale   |
| Sport      | skiing  | rowing   | badminton | snowboarding  |

