4. the person drinking juice is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the owner of the snake is between the person drinking lemonade and the owner of the rat##2
7. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
