3. the photographer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is the police-officer##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | photographer        | police-officer  | analyst | engineer   |
| Sport       | climbing | badminton | lacrosse    | sailing |
| Transport   | quad-bike        | helicopter     | jet-ski       | ship      |

