.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, kale, onion, lime
4 different pets are kept: turtle, lizard, snake, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, roller, car, van
1. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
2. the person eating orange is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person eating onion is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the van is the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the owner of the lizard is between the person eating lime and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | lime | kale | orange | onion |
| Pet         | turtle       | lizard     | snake   | goldfish   |
| Transport   | ship | roller | car | van |

 